  • Packages that use UnaCloudAbstractMessage 
    Package Description
    communication
    In this package are located all classes used to create udp communication message for Unacloud
    communication.messages
    In this package are located all classes which represents main messages and responses for TCP communication between control and agent programs.
    communication.messages.ao
    In this package are located all classes which represents request sent from server to process task in agent
    communication.messages.pmo
    In this package are located all classes which represents request sent from server to process task in physical machine
    communication.messages.vmo
    In this package are located all classes which represents request sent from server to process task in virtual machine executions
